{"title":"Edge 默认配置文件和 VSCode JavaScript Debugger 的 Edge 配置文件重名","uid":"51fb499ca555f736495b751e742c5e94","slug":"Edge-默认配置文件和-VSCode-debug-配置文件重名","date":"2023-12-25T07:30:20.000Z","updated":"2023-12-25T09:05:48.118Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Edge-默认配置文件和-VSCode-debug-配置文件重名.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"问题\"><a href=\"#问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题\"></a>问题</h2><p>从任务栏新建的 Edge 窗口使用的是其他配置文件。<br><img src=\"/post/Edge-%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C-VSCode-debug-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8D%E5%90%8D/edge_create_new_window.png\" alt=\"从任务栏中新建 Edge 窗口\"><br><img src=\"/post/Edge-%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C-VSCode-debug-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8D%E5%90%8D/edge_new_window.png\" alt=\"新窗口使用不同配置文件\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"原因\"><a href=\"#原因\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原因\"></a>原因</h2><p>任务栏上的 Edge 启动参数 <code>--profile-directory=Default</code> 中的配置文件和 VSCode JavaScript Debugger 调试用的 Edge 配置文件 <code>%APPDATA%\\Code\\User\\workspaceStorage\\...\\ms-vscode.js-debug\\.profile\\Default</code> 重名。</p>\n<h2 id=\"解决方式\"><a href=\"#解决方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决方式\"></a>解决方式</h2><ol>\n<li>将 <code>%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Microsoft\\Edge\\User Data\\Default</code> 中的 Default 配置文件改名，例如 <code>Profile 1</code></li>\n<li>将任务栏中快捷方式的启动参数改为新配置文件的名称，例如 <code>--profile-directory=&quot;Profile 1&quot;</code><br> <img src=\"/post/Edge-%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C-VSCode-debug-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8D%E5%90%8D/edge_shortcut_properties.png\" alt=\"查看任务栏快捷方式的属性\"><br> <img src=\"/post/Edge-%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C-VSCode-debug-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8D%E5%90%8D/edge_shortcut_change_properties.png\" alt=\"修改启动参数\"></li>\n</ol>\n","text":"问题从任务栏新建的 Edge 窗口使用的是其他配置文件。 原因任务栏上的 Edge 启动参数 --profile-directory=Default 中的配置文...","permalink":"/post/Edge-默认配置文件和-VSCode-debug-配置文件重名","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":365,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"VSCode","slug":"VSCode","count":2,"path":"api/tags/VSCode.json"},{"name":"Windows","slug":"Windows","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Windows.json"},{"name":"Edge","slug":"Edge","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Edge.json"},{"name":"JavaScript Debugger","slug":"JavaScript-Debugger","count":1,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript-Debugger.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">问题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">原因</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解决方式</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Jiahao","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"计算机系学生","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/TheJiahao","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VSCode 配置 clangd","uid":"bf8182607cfdb3b14d8fec4dc20a2905","slug":"Windows-下通过-Scoop-为-VSCode-配置-clangd","date":"2022-05-11T21:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-12-21T22:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows-下通过-Scoop-为-VSCode-配置-clangd.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"准备工作安装 Scoop shellInvoke-WebRequest get.scoop.sh | Invoke-Expression安装 Clangd安装 ...","permalink":"/post/Windows-下通过-Scoop-为-VSCode-配置-clangd","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":287,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编程","slug":"编程","count":1,"path":"api/categories/编程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"VSCode","slug":"VSCode","count":2,"path":"api/tags/VSCode.json"},{"name":"Windows","slug":"Windows","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Windows.json"},{"